item.ptxt:
MIL is turned on by command not only ECM but also TCM (A/T model). It is indistinguishable which module turns on MIL (for details of on-board diagnostic system for A/T model, refer to 
OBD System Description
). Therefore, check both ECM and TCM (A/T model) for DTC when MIL lights up. When checking ECM for DTC, keep in mind that DTC is displayed differently depending on the scan tool used.

